Start with CentOS Runtime
    centos:7
update all the cureent packages
    yum -y update
Install apache php php-gd php-mysql
    yum -y instal httpd php php-gd php-mysql
Configure apache httpd.conf
Copy the code form code folder - use either command ADD or COPY
    /var/www/html
Set DB env variables
Start apache
    httpd -D FOREGROUND